---
title: Halloumi Panzanella Salad with Caper Vinaigrette
description: This twist on the popular Tuscan salad brings classic ingredients: tomato, spinach, peppers and croutons, then tops them with golden-seared halloumi for major flavour!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/halloumi-panzanella-salad-55982d73.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/halloumi-panzanella-salad-6188d41a6175746c36157baa-542adbf3.pdf
